data.description: Welcome home.Classic floor plan offers a nicely updated & spacious eat-in kitchen with ample counters, natural cabinetry, stainless appliances & dining area, w sliders to sunny south facing deck. An inviting family room with fireplace & hardwood flooring is open to the large kitchen, the formal dining rooms  has crown molding, Custom french doors lead to the living room.1st floor laundry/half bath complete the first floor. Upstairs find four generous bedrooms including master with en suite bath & walk-in closet, with additional storage beyond. Wood and solid flooring though out. Everything is thought of, with a fully finished lower level that has in home office, a game room and a media room. plus a kids hideaway! 4 bedrooms 2.5 baths; 2 car garage and short path to neighborhood. Stone walls welcome guests, over sized driveway,.Back yard is level, fenced, & shaded setting.Look closely at the photos & virtual walk thru Matterport before show requests. Easy commuting location.
